ActNational Energy Board Act
National Energy Board Act Part VI (Oil and Gas) Regulations
SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-320 - Steelhead LNG (A) Inc.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-320 to Steelhead LNG (A) Inc. to export natural gas, in the form of liquefied natural gas, from a point at the outlet of the loading arm of proposed natural gas liquefaction terminals which are anticipated to be located near the village of Mill Bay, British Columbia.
